sec.p:
This research work deals with five (05) control strategies under variable climatic conditions:
Fuzzy-based MPPT control to track the maximum power point;
DC-DC converter control using duty cycle based on PI regulators;
DC-Bus control;
DC-AC inverter control;
Comparative study;
BSS energy management.

